 "name": "RPlog_Punishment",
 "title": "Punishment",
 "summary": "Admiral Axel Vichten's gaudy private Skipray Blastboat returns to the hangar, scratched up from a rough jungle trip, carrying the armored Baron Mygedo (Sekes), the Mandalorian Cantrell, and a captured Falleen and the erratic woman Decrevi. A foul-mooded Axel complains about the damage to his 'baby' while Cantrell needles him for turning a military vessel into a party boat. As the group disembarks, Cantrell observes that one of their number is lucky her superior had sense and compassion, but Axel coldly clarifies there was no compassion -- only the pragmatic need for every combatant they can get in the conflict to come. The terse scene shows the hard, transactional calculus of Axel's command.",
